(amụrụ n'April 8, 1981), nke a maara dị ka Honorable C.N.O.T.E., bụ onye America na-emepụta ihe ndekọ hip hop na onye na-ede égwu.
Mays malitere imepụta ihe mgbè ọ dị afọ iri na ise na Benton Harbor Area nke Michigan, tupu ọ kwaga Atlanta na 2006

O nwèrè ihe karịrị 7,000 placements na albums ma eleghị ányà a maara ya nke ọma màkà ịmepụta "New Level" site na rapper A$AP Ferg, yana egwu "M'$" site na onye rapper A $AP Rocky. Mays emepụtawokwa ọtụtụ egwu màkà ndị omenkà dị iche iche dịka 2 Chainz, Migos, Ne-Yo, Flo Rida, Gucci Mane, Travis Scott, Yo Gotti, Future, Meek Mill, na Trippie Redd na ndị ọzọ.
